		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Flour Mills Nigeria]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[General]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://fmnplc.com/?p=2101</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[<p>TOPFEEDS has been awarded the number one animal feeds brand in Nigeria in the recently concluded Made in Nigeria Brand Awards 2018. The award was given to TOPFEEDS to recognize the company’s contribution to agriculture in the country, especially in animal husbandry and its excellent service delivery. The Executive Registrar of the Made in Nigeria [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com/fmn-topfeeds-emerges-preferred-animal-feed-brand-2018/">FMN TOPFEEDS EMERGES THE MOST PREFERRED ANIMAL FEED BRAND IN 2018</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com">FMN</a>.</p>
]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>TOPFEEDS has been awarded the number one animal feeds brand in Nigeria in the recently concluded Made in Nigeria Brand Awards 2018.</p>
<p>The award was given to TOPFEEDS to recognize the company’s contribution to agriculture in the country, especially in animal husbandry and its excellent service delivery. The Executive Registrar of the Made in Nigeria Brand Awards, Desmond Esorougwe, said that TOPFEEDS stood out as a local brand with very high international quality. He also referred to the heritage of the company and its consistency in delivering excellence for over five decades since it was established in 1968.</p>
<p>Receiving the award, the company’s Managing Director, Mr. Anthony Ewing, expressed the company’s delight to be chosen. He reaffirmed the company’s position to continually improve its delivery of value to its customers and the nation as a whole. Also at the event were Austin Daylop, Olufemi Babawole and Eric Adeleye, the general manager sales and marketing, the regional manager West Region and the sales representative, Lagos and Otta respectively.</p>
<p>TOPFEEDS is the trading name of PREMIER FEED MILLS, a wholly owned subsidiary of FMN Plc.</p>
