		<title>FMN Strengthens partnership with Master Bakers</title>
		<link>https://fmnplc.com/fmn-strengthens-partnership-master-bakers/</link>
				<pubDate>Fri, 31 Aug 2018 11:40:13 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Flour Mills Nigeria]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[General]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://fmnplc.com/?p=2070</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[<p>FMN has always been passionate about supporting small and medium scale businesses in Nigeria. In the Bread and pastry industry, we work very closely with the association of master bakers and caterers of Nigeria (AMBCN) to ensure that our partners and downstream customers get the right type of support for their businesses. We constantly invest [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com/fmn-strengthens-partnership-master-bakers/">FMN Strengthens partnership with Master Bakers</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com">FMN</a>.</p>
]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>FMN has always been passionate about supporting small and medium scale businesses in Nigeria. In the Bread and pastry industry, we work very closely with the association of master bakers and caterers of Nigeria (AMBCN) to ensure that our partners and downstream customers get the right type of support for their businesses.<br />
We constantly invest in the development of innovative technology and in capacity development and knowledge sharing for our partner bakers. To this end we recently introduced 3 new Flour Varieties &#8211; whole wheat flour, Easy bake flour and Classic flour.<br />
The new flour varieties were introduced to the AMBCN at an interactive session that was held recently for Master Bakers, in Lagos.<br />
Speaking at the session, Mr. Paul Udochi, Head of Sales, B2B, for FMN informed that the decision to hold constant interactions with bakers was to create an avenue for constant interaction and engagement with bakers and customers. He also encouraged the bakers to retain their loyalty as customers and assured that the company will continue to deliver on the promise of quality to ensure their businesses always have an edge over competition.</p>
