								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Happiness is when we come together in participating in what we believe in. Sharing a bond of love and fun, that’s what human life is all about. As part of an employee engagement program, employees of FMN in Apapa recently participated in a series of skills acquisition activities that exposed them to the basics of baking. It was an obvious fun-filled day because it wasn’t just about ingredients, recipes and baking but the creativity and empowerment all coming together.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The program was divided into two major categories –Pastries and Bread making and was conducted at the Bakery at the R&amp;D department in FMN Apapa.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>At FMN, it’s always a Season of Love because Together Everyone Achieves More as we dispense happiness by quenching hunger.</p>
<p>So we say to everyone who participated, “Thanks for being Awesome”.</p>
