								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The NESG summit has over the years become a significant avenue for national discourse of the Nigerian economy, by the private and public sector. This year’s summit which is the 23<sup>rd</sup> in the series is themed, “Opportunities, productivity and employment: Actualizing the economic recovery and growth plan”.</p>
<p>Mr. John Coumantaros, the Chairman, Flour Mills of Nigeria Plc and the Head, Corporate Business Development, Mr. Sadiq Usman, led a delegate to this year’s event where they were actively involved in discussions focused on driving productivity in agriculture and manufacturing.</p>
