		<title>FMN Chairman Leads Plenary Session at the Second Edition Of the Kaduna Economic and Investment Summit</title>
		<link>https://fmnplc.com/fmn-chairman-leads-kaduna-economic-investment-summit/</link>
				<pubDate>Fri, 07 Apr 2017 15:33:13 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[General]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Press]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://fmnplc.com/?p=1570</guid>
				<description><![CDATA[<p>The Chairman, Flour Mills Group, Mr John Coumantaros was the first plenary speaker at the second Kaduna Economic and Investment Summit, KADINVEST 2.0. &#160; It was at this event that he announced an FMN project to set up a Fertilizer Blending Plant in Kaduna. The project was conceived to boost agriculture and increase the potential [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com/fmn-chairman-leads-kaduna-economic-investment-summit/">FMN Chairman Leads Plenary Session at the Second Edition Of the Kaduna Economic and Investment Summit</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com">FMN</a>.</p>
]]></description>
								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>The Chairman, Flour Mills Group, Mr John Coumantaros was the first plenary speaker at the second Kaduna Economic and Investment Summit, <strong>KADINVEST 2.0</strong>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>It was at this event that he announced an FMN project to set up a Fertilizer Blending Plant in Kaduna. The project was conceived to boost agriculture and increase the potential and production capacity of the state.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The FMN Group, which has not just been one of the major investors in Kaduna, but the country at large, was one of the major sponsors of the summit.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Mr John Coumantarous, in his presentation, also reeled out several strategic investment plans that the company has for the northern region especially in relation to the food and agro-allied value chain.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The summit which is scheduled to end today, 6th of April 2017 had in attendance notable stakeholders from several walks of life.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Emir of Kano and keynote speaker, His Highness, Muhammadu Sanusi II, spoke plainly about the troubles that have bedevilled the northern region but expressed optimism for platforms like <strong>KADINVEST 2.0</strong> that is already ushering the future.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Another landmark of the event was the signing of the <strong>Ease of Doing Business Charter</strong>, which will launch Kaduna state further into the business sphere and share of the country’s massive potential.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The Executive Governor of Kaduna State, Mallan Nasir El-Rufai, explained that KADINVEST 2.0 is the government’s commitment to ensuring that everything is being put in place to make business<u>es</u> thrive in the state.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The two-day event will come to a close today with a clear roadmap and the first steps to explore the potentials of the state and the country to their fullest.</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com/fmn-chairman-leads-kaduna-economic-investment-summit/">FMN Chairman Leads Plenary Session at the Second Edition Of the Kaduna Economic and Investment Summit</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://fmnplc.com">FMN</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
